These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, musical, zombie, mystery
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, helicopter, car, trike
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person watching crime movies is the person driving the trike##1
3. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
5. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre          | mystery | zombie | musical | crime   |
| Transport   | helicopter  | snowmobile     | car   | trike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, trance, country, r&b
House: cottage, victorian, farmhouse, gothic-revival
1. the fan of r&b is the victorian house##1
2. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
3. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
4. the fan of r&b is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
5. the victorian house is on the left of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | country | r&b | trance | rock    |
| House   | farmhouse    | victorian      | cottage | gothic-revival |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
House: townhouse, futuristic, cottage, ranch-style
There are 4 different nationalities: french, nigerian, australian, polish
1. the australian is on the left of the polish##1
2. the townhouse house is the french##1
3. the nigerian is on the far right##1
4. the polish is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
5. the cottage house is on the left of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| House         | townhouse | ranch-style | cottage   | futuristic |
| Nationality   | french   | australian | polish | nigerian         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, writer, architect, coach
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, hip-hop, folk, indie
1. the fan of hip-hop is the coach##1
2. the writer is on the left of the fan of folk##1
3. the writer is on the left of the freelancer##1
4. the writer is on the right of the coach##1
5. the fan of rock is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Job   | coach | writer | freelancer  | architect      |
| Music-Genre         | hip-hop | indie   | folk | rock |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, hot-chocolate, lemonade, coffee
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, grey, brown, lavender
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
4. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who likes brown##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Beverage   | coffee | lemonade | hot-chocolate | sprite |
| Color    | red       | lavender | brown | grey     |

