.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, bellflower, daisy, lily
House: palace, gothic-revival, colonial, townhouse
1. the person who growsbellflower is on the far right##1
2. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
3. the townhouse house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
4. the palace house is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
5. the townhouse house is on the right of the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Flower   | lily | daisy | daffodil | bellflower |
| House           | palace      | colonial | townhouse | gothic-revival    |

