.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, water, mirinda, hot-chocolate
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, family, zombie, scientific
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1
4. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking water is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage   | mirinda | water | fanta | hot-chocolate  |
| Movie-Genre           | zombie | time-travel | scientific       | family |

