.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, october, february, september
4 different pets are kept: dog, fish, cat, ferret
1. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the owner of the ferret is the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
5. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Birthday         | february | december      | october | september |
| Pet   | dog          | fish | cat     | ferret    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, march, june, september
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, golf, tennis, badminton
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Birthday   | march    | june       | april | september   |
| Sport     | golf | tennis | badminton   | baseball |

