.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, disco, ambient, r&b
4 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, snake, bird
1. the owner of the goat is on the right of the fan of disco##1
2. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of punk##1
3. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Music-Genre    | punk | ambient  | disco | r&b |
| Pet   | bird | snake | goldfish          | goat    |

