.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, august, march, may
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, game, blend, bolivar
1. the blend-smoker is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Birthday      | march | august  | october | may |
| Cigar   | siglo  | blend | bolivar           | game   |

