.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-12::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, balloon-flower, iris, tulip
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, june, march, december
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
2. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Flower   | balloon-flower | bellflower | tulip | iris  |
| Birthday           | december | june      | march | july |

