.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-13::.
4 different games are played: snooker, mah-jongg, bridge, go
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, june, august, february
1. the person who's birthday is in february is the person playing snooker##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
3. the person playing bridge is the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Game   | bridge | mah-jongg  | snooker | go   |
| Birthday        | august | june | february    | march |

