.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-14::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, go, poker, whist
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, light-blue, pink, black
1. the person playing scrabble is the person who likes light-blue##1
2. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
3. the person playing go is the person who likes pink##1
4. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
5. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |     4      |
| Game          | scrabble | poker  | go  | whist |
| Color   | light-blue   | amber | pink | black   |

