.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-18::.
There 4 different types of food: pepper, papaya, cucumber, tomato
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, badminton, volleyball, skateboarding
1. the person eating pepper is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
4. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
5. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Food      | pepper   | tomato | papaya   | cucumber      |
| Sport   | tennis | skateboarding      | badminton | volleyball |

