.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-19::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, indie, metal, salsa
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, bongani, ritmeester, aristoff
1. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
2. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
3. the ritmeester-smoker is the fan of metal##1
4. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
5. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre         | indie | metal | salsa | country |
| Cigar   | aristoff     | ritmeester    | dunhill      | bongani   |

