.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, basketball, golf, swimming
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, september, june, october
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Sport   | lacrosse | golf | basketball | swimming   |
| Birthday     | june  | july    | september       | october |

 